ZYLJ4eW04xY.description:
Quake II is a first-person shooter video game released in December 1997. It was developed by id Software and published by Activision. It is not a direct sequel to Quake; id decided to revert to an existing trademark when the game's fast-paced, tactile feel felt closer to a Quake game than a new franchise.[4] The game is followed by Quake IV.

My Facebook Page - http://www.facebook.com/glenntendo 

Quake 2 review on the nintendo 64. Recorded using a dazzle and on original real console hardware and game cartridge.

1lVNagNAu_s.title: STUDIO4FUN | La Grande Séance
1lVNagNAu_s.description:
La Grande Séance
http://www.grandeseance.com

La Grande Séance est une journée consacrée au réseautage, à léchange dinformation et à la pratique de la photographie de studio. Cest le rendez-vous que se donnent les différents artisans de limage, i.e. photographes, maquilleurs(euses), modèles, etc. 

Tout le monde y trouve son compte : les photographes rencontrent de nouveaux modèles, partagent trucs et astuces avec leurs pairs, font lessai de différents équipements déclairage, etc. Lapprentissage du médium photographique se faisant en grande partie à travers la pratique, la Grande Séance est l'opportunité idéale pour expérimenter et poser des questions sur place.

Les images vidéos ont été prises au cours de la 12e Grande Séance (14 novembre 2010). La Grande Séance est un événement trimestriel, et la 14e Grande Séance se tiendra le 6 février 2011. Pour plus d'information : http://www.grandeseance.com

Remerciement aux conférenciers, commanditaires et bénévoles qui ont grandement contribué au succès de cet événement.

3ySgAQoEXqk.title: Dark Link Destroyed (First 4 Figures)
3ySgAQoEXqk.description:
A few months ago I received my Dark Link Exclusive Figure from First 4 Figures.  Sadly when it arrived I noticed that it's head fell off in the box.  This destroyed the wires that connect to the head allowing the eyes to glow.

I contacted First 4 Figures about the problem as was told another would be made and sent my way.  Now that the new figure is made for me, I had to destroy the original damaged product so that this awesome collectable stays as rare as it was originally meant to be.

First 4 Figures is awesome because they really care about their customers.  I really appreciate their dedication to making sure their fans get working versions of their awesome collectables.  It's a shame I had to destroy Dark Link, but it had to be done.

Enjoy the video of me smashing Dark Link.

Also be sure to Follow Me on Twitter (@KingNintendoFan) and to Like my page on Facebook.

Twitter: http://twitter.com/KingNintendoFan/

Facebook: http://www.facebook.com/KingNintendoFanboy
